-upon-muttafaqun-alayhi","tag-assembly-al-majlis","tag-community-jamaah","tag-discouraged-al-makruh","tag-ease-al-yusr","tag-unlawful-al-haram","tag-manners-adab","tag-sitting-al-maqad"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-3Zj","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":2943,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/18\/people-wish-death-hour\/","url_meta":{"origin":15333,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Trials: People wish for death before the Hour","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Hour will not be established until a man passes by the grave of another man and he says: Would that I were in his place!\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7115, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 157 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9809,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/14\/many-women-few-men-hour\/","url_meta":{"origin":15333,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Signs: Many women, few men a sign of the Hour","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA time will come to people when a man will go around with gold to give in charity, but he will find no one to accept it, and a single man will be seen followed by forty women\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0