2014\/02\/17\/withdraw-from-misguidance\/","url_meta":{"origin":15333,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ruin: Withdraw from those leading Ummah astray","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe people will be ruined by a branch of the Quraysh tribe.\u201d They said, \u201cWhat do you command us to do?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIf only the people would withdraw from them.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3604,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13895,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/02\/wudu-broken-sound-smell\/","url_meta":{"origin":15333,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Ablution invalid by passing wind with sound, smell","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 2, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abbas ibn Tamim reported: My uncle asked the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, about a man who suspects that he passed wind during prayer. The Prophet said, \u201cHe should not leave his prayer unless he hears a sound or finds a smell.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 137,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15333","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"